  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/11174a550de66c7580566ae72ae71b6a.avif?t=1769568665\" width=1138 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🥤 <strong>▼ POP THE BEAT, SAVE THE WORLD ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PopSlinger</strong> is a vibrant, narrative-focused <i>musical shooter</i> inspired by the bold spirit of ‘80s and ‘90s <i>New Retro</i> culture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a world where style, rhythm, and soda-powered action collide in a neon-soaked adventure driven by music and heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💖 <strong>▼ A HEROINE IS BORN ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join <strong>Ria Carbon</strong>, a funky heroine on a stylish quest to save the world from sinister invaders spilling in from another dimension. Armed with soda-powered guns and unstoppable groove, Ria takes the fight straight to the source of the corruption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backing her up is <strong>Gin</strong>, a former PopSlinger heroine whose experience — and attitude — prove crucial as the battle escalates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/0d801a7c66923bf38b79f5614c4dc0fc.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/0d801a7c66923bf38b79f5614c4dc0fc.webm?t=1769568665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/50304da576e1d3d01d95c5b31857fc73.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" width=237 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/50304da576e1d3d01d95c5b31857fc73.webm?t=1769568665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Together, they face the <strong>Corazones</strong>: people whose hearts have been twisted and overtaken by dark forces from beyond reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/57147614a2d26b653fbca2398e7a6c87.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/57147614a2d26b653fbca2398e7a6c87.webm?t=1769568665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/ceb7452d6ad64044b91dacb7763238aa.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" width=212 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/ceb7452d6ad64044b91dacb7763238aa.webm?t=1769568665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/ceb7452d6ad64044b91dacb7763238aa.mp4?t=1769568665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/12b989552da8d9f213b5eb3aa26d384f.webp?t=1769568665\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/12b989552da8d9f213b5eb3aa26d384f.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" class=\"bb_img\" width=250 height=250 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨 <strong>▼ STYLE, STORY & SODA COLLIDE▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥤 <strong>Dreamy New Retro Visuals:</strong> Immerse yourself in an aesthetic inspired by 90’s Japanese animation, blending marker-style artwork with VHS-infused 2D sprites.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎙️ <strong>Fully Voiced Cutscenes:</strong> Hand-drawn, vibrantly animated portraits bring the story to life through expressive, fully voiced dialogue scenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💫 <strong>Whimsical Narrative:</strong> Experience an emotional, stylish story inspired by classic magical girl anime, Japanese films, and television from the 90s — loaded with visual flair and special effects.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔫 <strong>▼ SODA-POWERED ACTION ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash a <strong>soft-drink-powered magical arsenal</strong> as you blast through waves of enemies in rhythm-driven combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your performance shapes the experience: precision, timing, and flow all matter as you fight to reclaim corrupted hearts and restore harmony to the beat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/7c50ee989e7cdafed35b86a7297cd2af.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/7c50ee989e7cdafed35b86a7297cd2af.webm?t=1769568665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/7c50ee989e7cdafed35b86a7297cd2af.mp4?t=1769568665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎶 <strong>▼ GROOVE TO THE RHYTHM ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every encounter moves to the music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>fully dynamic soundtrack</strong> reacts to your in-game performance in real time, shifting and evolving as you shoot, dodge, and stay in sync. Inspired by an eclectic mix of genres — including <strong>Future Funk</strong>, <strong>New Jack Swing</strong>, and more — the soundtrack turns every battle into a living remix.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The better you play, the deeper the groove.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/4fb787c3011c7bfb0f800249b8eee84d.avif?t=1769568665\" width=1138 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>PopSlinger</strong>, it’s not just about shooting! It's about doing it with <strong>Style and Strategy!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your Oranger to hit enemies with the <strong>matching color</strong> to keep the rhythm alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>🎯 <strong>Land 4 shots of the same color</strong> to summon your<strong> Popping Powers! Each color brings Gin out to assist you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/b8baa98f1eaaaf38cd1e9098fc7a7efe.avif?t=1769568665\" width=724 height=330 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Pop 8 enemies in two matching sets</strong> to create a <strong>Color Progression!</strong> — this makes the <i>music change</i> instantly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/342f5aeb06d0e0034f4a8b5e78f64c89.webp?t=1769568665\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/342f5aeb06d0e0034f4a8b5e78f64c89.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" class=\"bb_img\" width=560 height=158 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep doing progressions to <strong>discover the whole track!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>8 of the same color leads to a Double Progression!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/9d5622fd6ed9cb565c08cdba430617a8.webp?t=1769568665\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/9d5622fd6ed9cb565c08cdba430617a8.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" class=\"bb_img\" width=560 height=158 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more combos you pull off, the more hype the music gets, and the higher rank you'll get! Get all you Rankmans!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/b46f756f446b422c9cc402c389fd1358.avif?t=1769568665\" width=916 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete specific combo sequences to unlock Dream Time! A hyper mode where Ria becomes invincible!! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/0b95ad6ccc37a2d41d5f94ef9fb6d038.avif?t=1769568665\" width=898 height=289 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The best PopSlingers are smart and nimble! Their destinies are set during the party!!!</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PopSlinger</strong> is a stylish, soda-powered musical adventure where rhythm fuels combat, emotion drives the story, and every shot pops to the beat.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥤 <strong>Developed by Funky Can Creative</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/11174a550de66c7580566ae72ae71b6a.avif?t=1769568665\" width=1138 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🥤 <strong>▼ POP THE BEAT, SAVE THE WORLD ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PopSlinger</strong> is a vibrant, narrative-focused <i>musical shooter</i> inspired by the bold spirit of ‘80s and ‘90s <i>New Retro</i> culture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a world where style, rhythm, and soda-powered action collide in a neon-soaked adventure driven by music and heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💖 <strong>▼ A HEROINE IS BORN ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join <strong>Ria Carbon</strong>, a funky heroine on a stylish quest to save the world from sinister invaders spilling in from another dimension. Armed with soda-powered guns and unstoppable groove, Ria takes the fight straight to the source of the corruption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backing her up is <strong>Gin</strong>, a former PopSlinger heroine whose experience — and attitude — prove crucial as the battle escalates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/0d801a7c66923bf38b79f5614c4dc0fc.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/0d801a7c66923bf38b79f5614c4dc0fc.webm?t=1769568665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app