ras/342f5aeb06d0e0034f4a8b5e78f64c89.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" class=\"bb_img\" width=560 height=158 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep doing progressions to <strong>discover the whole track!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>8 of the same color leads to a Double Progression!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/9d5622fd6ed9cb565c08cdba430617a8.webp?t=1769568665\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/9d5622fd6ed9cb565c08cdba430617a8.poster.avif?t=1769568665\" class=\"bb_img\" width=560 height=158 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more combos you pull off, the more hype the music gets, and the higher rank you'll get! Get all you Rankmans!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/b46f756f446b422c9cc402c389fd1358.avif?t=1769568665\" width=916 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete specific combo sequences to unlock Dream Time! A hyper mode where Ria becomes invincible!! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928320/extras/0b95ad6ccc37a2d41d5f94ef9fb6d038.avif?t=1769568665\" width=898 height=289 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The best PopSlingers are smart and nimble! Their destinies are set during the party!!!</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PopSlinger</strong> is a stylish, soda-powered musical adventure where rhythm fuels combat, emotion drives the story, and every shot pops to the beat.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥤 <strong>Developed by Funky Can Creative</strong></p>",
